🏦 AI-Native SDLC Platform — Enterprise Architecture (JPMC-Ready)

1. 🎯 Objective

Design and implement an AI-driven, event-orchestrated SDLC platform that transforms software delivery into a:

Continuous, autonomous, governed, and auditable pipeline
from HLDD → Jira → Code → Review → Deploy → Validate

⸻

2. 🧱 Architectural Principles

These are critical for enterprise approval:

🔹 1. Human-in-Control (NOT fully autonomous)

* AI acts under policy + supervision
* Critical gates (merge, prod deploy) remain controlled

🔹 2. Event-Driven Architecture

* No direct agent-to-agent calls
* All interactions via:
    * Webhooks
    * Event bus

🔹 3. Orchestrator-Centric Control

* Single decision engine
* Prevents:
    * infinite loops
    * conflicting actions

🔹 4. Policy-as-Code Governance

* Every action validated through:
    * RBAC
    * policy engine

🔹 5. Full Observability & Auditability

* Every step:
    * logged
    * traceable
    * reproducible

⸻

