8. ⚠️ Risks & Mitigations

Risk	Impact	Mitigation
Hallucinated code	High	Test + validation agent
Infinite loops	High	Max iteration limit
Wrong task breakdown	Medium	Human override
Security leak	Critical	Data masking
Tool failure	Medium	Retry + fallback

